high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Pick up a knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the round table in the corner.
Cut the lettuce on the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the table.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the slice of lettuce in the sink.
Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Put the slice of lettuce on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of lettuce on the counter by the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter to the right of the sink
Grab the large knife off of the counter
Turn around and go to the round table
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices
Put the knife onto the table
Grab a slice of lettuce
Turn around and go to the sink
Wash the lettuce in the sink and take it out
Move to the left of the lettuce
Put the lettuce on the counter
anns.task_desc: Putting clean sliced lettuce on a counter

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter on the far right end of the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife on the counter
Turn around and go to the round wooden table on the left.
Slice the lettuce between the bread and another lettuce on the table.
Place the knife on the table in front of the bread.
Pick up the end piece of the lettuce
Turn around and go to the front of the sink.
Remove the lettuce from the sink after washing it under running water.
Move over left to the counter next to the sink.
Place the lettuce on the top of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed end piece of the lettuce on the counter.
